Description: Sixteen small unplaced fragments of papyrus bearing Hieratic text.
Curator's comments: These fragments added during 2013-2014. Larger papyrus (10052.1 published: Kitchen, Ram. Insc. Vol 6 p. 767. A. Theodorides, Le sermente terminale de “vérité-mensonge”, RdE 21, p. 96 (4, 14). A. Theodorides, La Notion égyptienne de possession exprimée par la locution prépositive m-di, RdE 22, p. 141 (3, 20-21). A. Cabrol, Les voies processionnelles de Thebes, OLA 97, (2001), p. 567-571. Rde: 13, 58, 9). To be republished by CJ Eyre and M Collier (agreed 2006)
Half of the unplaced fragments seem to come from EA10042 (and some possibly from 10053 and 10054 also) (Mark Collier, pers. comm).
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (380850) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/380850)
